	* configure.in: require glib >= 2.6.0.
	* testing/gda-diagnose.c (main):
	* testing/gda-test-models.c (main):
	* testing/gda-test-sql.c (main):
	use functions g_mkdir() and access() to stay compatible with
	glib 2.6.

